<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Welcome to Our Waitlist - Fifty Firsts Wellness</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=League+Spartan:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Quicksand', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        .email-header {
            padding: 32px 40px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-img {
            height: 60px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .social-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .social-icon svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .email-content {
            padding: 36px 40px;
        }

        .content-title {
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .content-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .exclusive-badge {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 12px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .waitlist-box {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-left: 3px solid #00969b;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 12px 0;
        }

        .waitlist-title {
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #00969b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .benefits-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .benefits-list li {
            padding: 4px 0;
            color: #374151;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 20px;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .benefits-list li:before {
            content: "•";
            color: #00969b;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }

        .contact-info {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-left: 3px solid #00969b;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .contact-title {
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #00969b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .contact-text {
            color: #374151;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #00969b;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer-copyright {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-top: 24px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }

            .email-header {
                padding: 24px 20px 20px;
            }

            .logo-img {
                height: 60px;
            }

            .social-icons {
                gap: 8px;
            }

            .social-icon {
                width: 18px;
                height: 18px;
            }

            .email-content {
                padding: 32px 20px;
            }

            .content-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .email-footer {
                padding: 24px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-container">
            <div class="email-header">
                
                <p class="greeting">Dear <%= firstName || 'Future Member' %>,</p>

                <p class="content-text">
                    Thank you for joining our waitlist! You're now part of an exclusive group that will be the first to experience our upcoming wellness products and services.
                </p>

                <div class="exclusive-badge">
                    VIP Early Access Member
                </div>

                <div class="waitlist-box">
                    <div class="waitlist-title">What to Expect</div>
                    <ul class="benefits-list">
                        <li>Early access to new wellness products</li>
                        <li>Exclusive previews and beta testing opportunities</li>
                        <li>Special launch pricing and offers</li>
                        <li>Priority support and personalized guidance</li>
                        <li>Behind-the-scenes updates on our development</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <p class="content-text">
                    We're working hard to bring you innovative wellness solutions that will transform your midlife journey. You'll be among the first to know when we're ready to launch!
                </p>

                <p class="content-text">
                    Thank you for your patience and trust in our mission to revolutionize wellness for people in their fifties and beyond.
                </p>

                <p class="content-text">
                    <strong>Welcome to the future of wellness!</strong>
                </p>

                <div class="contact-info">
                    <div class="contact-title">Questions About the Waitlist?</div>
                    <div class="contact-text">
                        Contact us at <%= companyEmail || 'info@fiftyfirstswellness.co.uk' %>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="content-text" style="margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                    Thanks,<br>
                    Fifty Firsts Wellness Team
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="email-footer">
                <div class="footer-text">
                    Questions or FAQ? Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@fiftyfirstswellness.co.uk" class="footer-link">info@fiftyfirstswellness.co.uk</a>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-copyright">
                    © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Fifty Firsts Wellness. All rights reserved.<br>
                    <% if (typeof unsubscribeUrl !== 'undefined') { %>
                        <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>" class="footer-link">Leave Waitlist</a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
